                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.63/360</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Parker</persName>, representing
                        American interests, to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-02-10T12:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 10, 1917, 12 noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>674. Department’s 657, February 8, four p.m. Am working on matter but see no
                    prospect of withdrawal or extension.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Parker</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
